    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Journey into the magical world of Epica and compete against other players from around the world in the rankings.   </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A fantasy adventure &amp; exploration game.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic combat </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crafting &amp; trading</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Global rankings </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hardcore mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam achievements </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >State of Epica</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is accessible during Early Access, the core development stage. The game went through several major updates, including the upgrade from Unreal Engine 4 to 5, and newer changes preparing the game for multiplayer.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The current scope centers on bringing the starting zone (Act 1) to life, which includes:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Player skills</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Player gear </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various world locations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Character development</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quests</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
